M|Opti|tx|Reduce SVG coordinate precision to decrease file size. The optimal precision depends on the viewBox size, but in general reducing precision shd be considered.
M|Opti|**In|**
M|Opti|tx|```svg
M|Opti|tx|<path d="M 10.293847 20.847362 L 30.938472 40.192837" />
M|Opti|tx|```
M|Opti|**Co|**
M|Opti|tx|```svg
M|Opti|tx|<path d="M 10.3 20.8 L 30.9 40.2" />
M|Opti|tx|```
M|Opti|**Au|**
M|Opti|tx|```bash
M|Opti|tx|npx svgo --precision=1 --multipass icon.svg
M|Opti|tx|```